            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1582199879768-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>arborio rice</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> to the<strong> </strong>pan, stirring to coat the grains of rice in the oil</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and stir continuously until the rice has absorbed most of the tomato juice</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1582199883973-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1582199883973-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1582199883973-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1582199883973-x1000.jpg",
